&lt;p&gt;And indeed, there are unused/redundant code which I can safely remove to clean up the codebase.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;End Note&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You probably heard about functional programming and the reasons of using it. Perhaps this will make you want to use functional programming even more. You do not have to refactor the entire codebase into a functional oriented codebase, it’s more about writing code that is easier to reason about.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Up until next time!&lt;/p&gt;
